const terms_en =
"&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:18pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#333333&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Terms and Conditions&nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt; &nbsp;&lt;/h2&gt; &lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:15pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#333333&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;1-Object&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#4a4a4a&quot;&gt;The purpose of this agreement is to define the conditions under which Tip&amp;Go provides the cardholder with electronic payment services in return for a fee defined in Article 10 hereof.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#4a4a4a&quot;&gt;These payment services include:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;ul&gt; &lt;li style=&quot;list-style-type:disc&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#4a4a4a&quot;&gt;opening and management of payment accounts,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li style=&quot;list-style-type:disc&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#4a4a4a&quot;&gt;to the credit of the payment account: recording of funds transferred by cards or by any other means of payment accepted by the Provider; receipt of transfers&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li style=&quot;list-style-type:disc&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#4a4a4a&quot;&gt;The provider has mandated the platform to facilitate the conclusion of the present contract with each account holder and to accompany them throughout their relationship with the provider. The provider does not offer any foreign exchange services.The provider has mandated the platform to facilitate the conclusion of the present agreement with each account Holder and to accompany them throughout their relationship with the provider.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:15pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#333333&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;2. Subscription to services&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#4a4a4a&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;2.1. Terms and conditions of subscription&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#4a4a4a&quot;&gt;The agreement is concluded remotely, according to the terms and conditions provided by the platform in the general conditions of the site. In order to conclude the online framework agreement, the applicant must have the equipment (hardware and software), for which he/she is solely responsible.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#4a4a4a&quot;&gt;By default, the acceptance of the framework contract is carried out remotely via the site and is materialized by an electronic signature. The applicant may request to sign the contract by hand. To this end, he/she must print the present contract, sign it, and return it electronically to the platform&#39;s customer service department whose contact information is indicated in the site&#39;s general conditions.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#4a4a4a&quot;&gt;In the event of a handwritten signature, the date of conclusion of the framework agreement shall be deemed to be the date indicated thereon and in the absence of such date, it shall be deemed to be the date of receipt of the framework agreement by the platform.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#4a4a4a&quot;&gt;The electronic signature of the framework agreement is performed through the site. The date of conclusion of the framework agreement is the date on which the applicant completes the electronic signature process as indicated on the site.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#4a4a4a&quot;&gt;The framework agreement concluded between the parties by electronic means has the same legal value as a paper-based framework agreement.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:15pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#333333&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;3. Opening an account&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#4a4a4a&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;3.1 Necessary conditions and prerequisites for the opening of the account&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#4a4a4a&quot;&gt;Any natural person who is at least eighteen (18) years of age and legally capable and a resident of Quebec.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#4a4a4a&quot;&gt;The holder declares at the time of the transmission of its application to the platform and throughout the duration of the framework contract:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#4a4a4a&quot;&gt;- he/she is at least 18 years of age&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#4a4a4a&quot;&gt;- that he/she is acting on his/her own behalf; and that all information provided at the time of registration is true, accurate and up-to-date.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#4a4a4a&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;3.2. Registration and Account opening procedure&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#4a4a4a&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;3.2.1. Information and supporting documents&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#4a4a4a&quot;&gt;All holders must provide Tip&amp;Go with the information and documents listed below, using the subscription form,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#4a4a4a&quot;&gt;The prospect agrees to provide information and documents related to his or her status as a hotel employee, first name, last name, email address, bank account number, transit number, etc.&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#4a4a4a&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;3.2.2. Limitations of the payment account&nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#4a4a4a&quot;&gt;At&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#4a4a4a&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt; &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#4a4a4a&quot;&gt;Tip&amp;Go&#39;s discretion, the use of a payment account may be limited without Tip&amp;go having to justify its decision to the holder concerned.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#4a4a4a&quot;&gt;The operation of the payment account shall be restricted if the holder has not provided all the information and documents required by Tip&amp;Go, as listed in point 3.2.1.&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#4a4a4a&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;3.2.3. Finalization of the registration&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#4a4a4a&quot;&gt;After entering into the framework agreement, the holder shall provide all the information and supporting documents requested by Tip&amp;Go. By agreeing to the terms of the framework contract, the holder agrees that Tip&amp;Go may transmit to the service provider his application for registration as holder and all supporting documents received by him.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#4a4a4a&quot;&gt;Tip&amp;Go shall be the only party entitled to accept the registration of a prospect as holder of a payment account in his name. Tip&amp;Go shall notify the holder of this agreement by any means in accordance with the procedures set out on the site.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#4a4a4a&quot;&gt;Tip&amp;go shall be entitled to refuse an application to open an account, without giving any reasons or entitling the holder to compensation. Tip&amp;go shall notify the Holder of such refusal by any means in accordance with the procedures set out on the site.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:15pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#333333&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;4. Operation of the payment account&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#4a4a4a&quot;&gt;The sums credited to the payment account result from funds transferred by card (or by any other means of payment accepted by Tip&amp;Go), or from the receipt of a transfer. These sums result from: the execution of a payment order to an account opened in the books of a third party payment service provider, the deduction by Tip&amp;Go of the charges due by the holder under the framework agreement or, the reversal of a transaction by card (or by any other means of payment).&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#4a4a4a&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;4.1. Acquisition of card payment orders on the payment account&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#4a4a4a&quot;&gt;The payment account may be funded by card (or any other means accepted by Tip&amp;Go), in one or more instalments. When the user wishes to carry out such an operation, he/she shall identify himself/herself on the site by indicating his/her user name (valid e-mail address) and his/her password.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#4a4a4a&quot;&gt;The funds transfer order is entered on a dedicated payment page. For any payment, the user may be asked to enter a single-use code notified on his cell phone to the card issuer. If necessary, Tip&amp;go may refuse any payment at its own discretion and without this decision giving rise to any compensation. The transfer of funds shall be carried out by the card issuer. Any dispute concerning such a transfer must be notified to the said institution. Tip&amp;Go shall not be entitled to cancel such a transfer.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#4a4a4a&quot;&gt;The cardholder is hereby informed that the acceptance of a card payment order by Tip&amp;Go does not guarantee the receipt of the corresponding funds by the cardholder on his account. The entry of the funds in the Holder&#39;s payment account shall be conditional upon the actual receipt by Tip&amp;Go of the funds collected minus the fees agreed upon in the terms of this contract.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#4a4a4a&quot;&gt;If the funds are not received for technical reasons, Tip&amp;go shall do everything in its power to regularise the operation. If the funds are not received for any other reason, Tip&amp;go shall inform the user as soon as possible of its inability to credit the account with the expected amount, so that the user can contact the holder.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#4a4a4a&quot;&gt;In the event that the transfer of funds to the cardholder&#39;s Account is cancelled by the card issuer following a dispute by the user, the cardholder agrees that Tip&amp;Go may cancel any funds transfer transaction for the corresponding amount.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#4a4a4a&quot;&gt;The holder acknowledges that such a dispute may be brought to the attention of the card issuer until the expiry of a maximum period of thirteen (13) months following the date on which the account to which the said card is linked is debited. Tip&amp;go shall be entitled to suspend or cancel any payment transaction initiated by the holder or an authorised representative, or, where applicable, to take the place of the holder and to recover the sums owed by the user, by any means, in the absence of sufficient funds on the account to make such a reversal.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#4a4a4a&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;4.2 Receipt of transfer to the Payment Account&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#4a4a4a&quot;&gt;The cardholder instructs Tip&amp;Go to receive transfer transactions in Canadian dollars from a bank or payment account opened in the books of a third party.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#4a4a4a&quot;&gt;The funds shall be credited to the holder&#39;s payment account by Tip&amp;Go as soon as possible after their actual receipt by the provider.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#4a4a4a&quot;&gt;After the funds have been credited to the holder&#39;s payment account, Tip&amp;Go shall provide the holder with a summary of the transfer transaction received, including the following information: the reference of the payment transaction, a reference enabling the payer to be identified, the amount of the transaction and the date of the payment.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:15pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#333333&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;5. Report&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#4a4a4a&quot;&gt;In his personal space, the holder has a statement of the payment transactions made on the payment account. The holder is invited to carefully read the list of these transactions. For each transfer transaction carried out by Tip&amp;Go, the holder shall have the following information: the reference number of the transaction, the identification of the beneficiary, the amount of the transaction, the date of receipt of the order and, where applicable, the charges relating to the execution of this transaction.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:15pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#333333&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;6. Payment Account Access and Personalized Security Data Privacy&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#4a4a4a&quot;&gt;The payment account can be accessed online in the personal area by means of identification data and in accordance with the requested authentication procedure (or strong authentication as the case may be).&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#4a4a4a&quot;&gt;Registrant shall provide identifying information. Each registrant agrees not to use the name or identifying information of any other person. The registrant is solely responsible for any use of his/her credentials. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt; &lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#4a4a4a&quot;&gt;Each entitled person is solely responsible for maintaining the confidentiality of his or her credentials, as well as any other personalized security data that may be assigned by the provider or Platform. Registrant shall take all reasonable steps to maintain the confidentiality and security of its personalized security data. The registrant also agrees to educate authorized persons about the confidentiality and security of their own personalized security data.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#4a4a4a&quot;&gt;Registrant agrees not to share their personalized security data with third parties.&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:15pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#333333&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;7. Opposition to personalized security data&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#4a4a4a&quot;&gt;The account holder must inform Tip&amp;Go of the loss or theft of his/her personalized security data, of the misappropriation or of any unauthorized use of his/her personal space or of the data linked to it as soon as he/she becomes aware of it in order to request that it be blocked. The holder is asked to declare:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#4a4a4a&quot;&gt;- directly by e-mail through the contact form available on the site. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;mailto:admin@tip-go.com&quot; style=&quot;text-decoration:none&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#0563c1&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;admin@tip-go.com&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#4a4a4a&quot;&gt; or through the platform, the loss of data and Tip@Go will immediately execute the request for opposition. The event will be recorded and time-stamped. A time-stamped stop payment number will be communicated to the holder. Tip&amp;Go will send a written confirmation of the stop payment to the concerned holder by e-mail. Tip&amp;go shall take charge of the file from an administrative point of view and shall keep all traces of the event for eighteen (18) months. The service provider shall not be held liable for the consequences of an objection by e-mail which does not originate from the holder.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#4a4a4a&quot;&gt;A request for opposition shall be deemed to have been made on the date and time of actual receipt of the request by Tip&amp;Go. In the event of theft of the personalised security data or fraudulent use of the personal space, Tip&amp;Go shall be entitled to request, via the platform, a receipt or a copy of the complaint from the holder, who undertakes to respond as soon as possible.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:15pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#333333&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;8. Blocking of the payment account and denial of access to the payment account&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#4a4a4a&quot;&gt;Tip&amp;Go reserves the right to block the payment account for objectively justified reasons relating to the security of the account, in the event of suspected unauthorised or fraudulent use of the payment account or in the event of a significantly increased risk that the holder will be unable to fulfil his obligation to pay the charges due under this framework agreement.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#4a4a4a&quot;&gt;The cardholder is hereby informed that Tip&amp;Go may deny access to the payment account to a third party providing payment initiation or account information services, for objectively motivated or documented reasons related to unauthorized or fraudulent access to the payment account by such provider, including unauthorized or fraudulent initiation of a payment transaction.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#4a4a4a&quot;&gt;In such cases, the holder will be informed in his personal space of the blocking or refusal of access to the payment account, and of the reasons for such blocking or refusal. This information shall be communicated to him, if possible, before the payment account is blocked or access is denied and at the latest immediately after the blocking or denial, unless the giving of this information can be communicated for objective security reasons. Tip&amp;Go shall unblock the account or restore access to it as soon as the reasons for blocking or refusing access no longer exist. The holder may request the unblocking of the account at any time by contacting Tip&amp;Go&#39;s customer service department, the details of which are given in the general terms and conditions of the site. The holder may have to create new identification data.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:15pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#333333&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;9. Contesting a transaction&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#4a4a4a&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;9.1. Provisions common to all holders&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#4a4a4a&quot;&gt;For any complaint relating to the payment transactions carried out by Tip&amp;Go within the framework of the present agreement, the holder is invited to contact the customer service department at the e-mail address indicated for this purpose in the general conditions of the site.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#4a4a4a&quot;&gt;A fee indicated in the pricing conditions may be charged in the event of an unjustified dispute of a transaction.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:15pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#333333&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;10. Processing fees&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#4a4a4a&quot;&gt;The services provided hereunder shall be charged by Tip&amp;Go in accordance with the tariff conditions. i.e. 15% on the amount of the tip plus applicable taxes.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#4a4a4a&quot;&gt;Payments (transfers) will be made on the Thursday following the work week performed (sunday to saturday).&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#4a4a4a&quot;&gt;All processing fees charged by the holder are automatically deducted from the payment account by Tip&amp;Go.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:15pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#333333&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;11. Duration and termination&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#4a4a4a&quot;&gt;The framework contract is concluded for an indefinite period. It comes into force as of its acceptance by the holder.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#4a4a4a&quot;&gt;The latter may terminate the framework agreement at any time by giving thirty (30) calendar days&#39; notice. Tip&amp;Go may terminate the framework agreement at any time by giving seven (7) days&#39; notice. In that event, the charges for the payment services shall be calculated on the basis of the tips accumulated during the period up to the date of termination.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#4a4a4a&quot;&gt;Each party shall send its notice of termination of this agreement to the other party by email as set forth in the site terms and conditions.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#4a4a4a&quot;&gt;As a result, the entire master agreement is terminated and the Payment Account is closed. The credit of the account will be transferred within two (2) months to the holder&#39;s bank account after deduction of the fees of and payable to the provider. If the credit of the payment account exceeds the limit indicated in the tariff Conditions, the amount exceeding this limit shall be transferred within thirty (30) days of the effective date of termination to the Holder&#39;s bank account after deduction of the fees due and payable to Tip&amp;Go. The provider shall be relieved of any obligation once it has confirmed to the Holder the transfer to the bank account indicated.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#4a4a4a&quot;&gt;In the event of serious breaches, fraud or non-payment by the holder, Tip&amp;Go reserves the right to suspend or terminate the present contract by sending an e-mail accompanied by a registered letter with acknowledgement of receipt without reason or notice.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#4a4a4a&quot;&gt;It is intended that the master agreement will be automatically terminated in the event of new circumstances affecting the ability of a party to enter into the agreement.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:15pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#333333&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;12. Modification of the contract&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#4a4a4a&quot;&gt;Tip&amp;Go reserves the right, at any time, to amend the framework agreement. Any draft amendment to the framework agreement shall be provided to the holder by Tip&amp;Go.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#4a4a4a&quot;&gt;In the event of refusal by the cardholder, such refusal will result in the termination of the master agreement at no cost, as well as the transfer of the balance of the payment account within one (1) month of the effective date of termination to cover any future disputes.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#4a4a4a&quot;&gt;Any legislative or regulatory provisions that would make it necessary to modify the master agreement or part of the master agreement will be applicable as soon as they come into force, without prior notice. The holder will however be informed.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#4a4a4a&quot;&gt;If the unique identifier or any other information necessary for the execution of a payment transaction provided by the cardholder is inaccurate, Tip&amp;Go shall not be liable for the improper execution of said Service.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:15pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#333333&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;13. Limitation of liability of Tip&amp;go&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#4a4a4a&quot;&gt;Tip&amp;Go shall not intervene in any way in the legal and commercial relations and possible disputes between the holder and the client or between the holder and the bank. Tip&amp;Go shall not exercise any control over the conformity, security, lawfulness, characteristics and appropriateness of the products and services which are the subject of a payment transaction.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#4a4a4a&quot;&gt;Each transaction carried out by the holder shall give rise to a contract directly between him and a client to whom Tip&amp;Go is not attached. Tip&amp;Go shall therefore not be held liable for the non-performance or improper performance of the resulting obligations, nor for any damage caused to the holder.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:15pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#333333&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;14. Commitments of the holder&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#4a4a4a&quot;&gt;The holder guarantees that no element of his personal space infringes on the rights of third parties or is contrary to the law, public order or morality.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt; &lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#4a4a4a&quot;&gt;He/she undertakes not to :&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;ol&gt; &lt;li style=&quot;list-style-type:decimal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#4a4a4a&quot;&gt;(i) Perform the master agreement in an unlawful manner or under conditions that could damage, disable, overburden or impair the site;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li style=&quot;list-style-type:decimal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#4a4a4a&quot;&gt;(ii) Impersonate another person or entity, falsify or conceal his or her identity, age or create a false identity;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li style=&quot;list-style-type:decimal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#4a4a4a&quot;&gt;(iii) Disseminate personal data or information relating to a third party, such as postal addresses, telephone numbers, e-mail addresses, credit card numbers, etc. In the event of a breach of its obligations, Tip&amp;Go shall be entitled to take all appropriate measures to put an end to the conduct concerned. It shall also be entitled to suspend, delete and/or block the holder&#39;s access to his account.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li style=&quot;list-style-type:decimal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#4a4a4a&quot;&gt;(iv) Without prejudice to legal actions brought by third parties, Tip&amp;Go shall be entitled to bring any legal action in its own right to compensate for any damage it may have suffered as a result of the holder&#39;s failure to fulfil its obligations under this contract.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ol&gt; &lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#4a4a4a&quot;&gt;If the holder notices a breach of the above obligations, he is invited to inform Tip&amp;Go by e-mail: admin@tip-go.com.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#4a4a4a&quot;&gt;Unless otherwise provided for by law and regulation, the data will not be kept beyond the effective date of termination of the contract. In particular, it is specified that personal data relating to the identification of the holder will be kept for a period of five (5) years from the end of the contractual relationship, in accordance with the applicable regulations on the fight against money laundering and the financing of terrorism.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#4a4a4a&quot;&gt;Data subjects have the following rights with respect to their data, in accordance with the conditions set forth in the regulations: right of access, right of rectification, right of opposition, right to erasure, right to limitation of processing and right to portability. A data subject may exercise his or her rights at any time by contacting the platform&#39;s customer service. His or her request must indicate his or her name, first name, and identifier, and be accompanied by a photocopy of an identity document bearing his or her signature.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#4a4a4a&quot;&gt;A reply will be sent to the person concerned within one (1) month of receipt of the request.&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:15pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#333333&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;15. Protection of personal data&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#4a4a4a&quot;&gt;The provider collects and processes any personal data in accordance with the applicable regulations governing the protection of such data, and in particular in compliance with the applicable law.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#4a4a4a&quot;&gt;The personal data required at the time of subscription is necessary for the services provided hereunder. Failure to provide the required personal data may result in the applicant being denied access to the services.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#4a4a4a&quot;&gt;The data subject is informed that personal data is collected for the following purposes in particular: the provision of the services provided as described herein; the fight against money laundering and the financing of terrorism; the processing of requests for information and complaints; the production of statistics. This processing is necessary for the execution of the framework contract as well as for compliance with legal obligations to which the data controllers are subject.&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#4a4a4a&quot;&gt;Personal data will not be passed on to any third party without the express consent of the persons concerned. However, personal data shall be transmitted to subcontractors of Tip&amp;Go, for the aforementioned purposes. The said subcontractors shall only act on the instructions of the holder.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:15pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#333333&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;16. Intellectual Property&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#4a4a4a&quot;&gt;Tip&amp;Go shall retain full ownership of the titles and property rights of any kind associated with the services offered to the holder. None of these property rights shall be transferred to the holder hereunder.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:15pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#333333&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;17. Death of the holder and inactive accounts&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#4a4a4a&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;17.1. Death of the holder&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#4a4a4a&quot;&gt;The death of the holder as soon as it is brought to the knowledge of the provider, puts an end to the framework contract. The operations taking place after the death are, except with the agreement of the rightful claimants or of the notary in charge of the estate, considered as not having been authorized.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#4a4a4a&quot;&gt;The payment account remains open as long as it takes to settle the estate and the service provider pays the balance with the agreement of the heirs or the notary in charge of the estate.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#4a4a4a&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;17.2. Inactive accounts&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#4a4a4a&quot;&gt;Any inactive account may be notified of inactivity by e-mail by Tip&amp;Go followed by a reminder one (1) month later. The holder&#39;s payment account shall be deemed to be inactive when, at the end of a period of twelve (12) months, it has not been the subject of any transaction (except for the deduction of management fees) at the initiative of the holder (or any authorised representative) and the holder has not contacted Tip&amp;Go in any form whatsoever.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#4a4a4a&quot;&gt;In the absence of a response or use of the balance credited to the account within this period, Tip&amp;Go may freeze and/or close the account and keep it open for the sole purpose of transferring the amounts due to the account indicated by the holder. In the event of death, the balance shall only be refunded to the rightful claimants of the holder.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#4a4a4a&quot;&gt;No execution or payment transactions can be made on the said account.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:15pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#333333&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;18. Force majeure&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#4a4a4a&quot;&gt;The parties shall not be liable, or deemed to have failed, under this agreement for any delay or failure to perform when caused by force majeure as defined in the Civil Code.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:15pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#333333&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;19. Protection of funds&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#4a4a4a&quot;&gt;The holder&#39;s funds shall be deposited, at the end of the working day following the day on which they were received by Tip&amp;Go, in a segregated account opened in the books of a bank under the conditions required by the regulations. The funds collected shall be protected and shall not form part of the institution&#39;s assets in terms of electronic money in the event of liquidation or bankruptcy of the company.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:15pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#333333&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;20. Complaints and mediation&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#4a4a4a&quot;&gt;The holder is invited to contact Tip&amp;Go&#39;s customer service department, which may be indicated on the site, for any complaint.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#4a4a4a&quot;&gt;Any complaint other than that provided for in Article 10 relating to the conclusion, performance or termination of the framework agreement must be notified by e-mail to the following address: admin@tip-go.com&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#4a4a4a&quot;&gt;The holder agrees that Tip&amp;Go may respond to his complaints on a durable medium. The reply shall be sent as soon as possible and at the latest within fifteen (15) working days following receipt of the complaint by Tip&amp;Go. However, it is sometimes possible that, for reasons beyond its control, Tip&amp;Go is unable to respond within this period of fifteen (15) working days.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#4a4a4a&quot;&gt;In this case, it will communicate to the holder a response specifying the reasons for this additional delay as well as the date on which it will send the final response. In any case, the holder will receive a final response within thirty (30) days at the latest.&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:15pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#4a4a4a&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;21-Tax return&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#4a4a4a&quot;&gt;It is understood that Tip@Go offers a tip collection service to hotel employees. Consequently, Tip@Go is not and will not be responsible for the amounts received by the cardholder. The amounts received by the cardholder may be taxable and the cardholder agrees to be fully responsible for and to keep track of such amounts.&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;h2&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/h2&gt; &lt;h2&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/h2&gt;"
